Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Located in Central West Region of NSW

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE Agribusiness is pleased to present for sale Bergen Park and Warili, two large-scale irrigated and dryland cropping properties in the renowned Central West Region of New South Wales.
Comprising approximately 3,899 hectares, Bergen Park and Warili are strategically located 16* lineal kilometres from one another, just 32* lineal kilometres south-west of Forbes in an area well regarded for cropping and horticultural production. 

Key features of the opportunity include:

‘Bergen Park’, Newell Highway, Forbes NSW 2871

•	Large-scale irrigated & dryland cropping property comprising 2,788* hectares with extensive frontage to the Newell Highway.

•	First class irrigation development with 591Ha* of laser levelled flood irrigation, 59Ha* of flood irrigation, 1,018* of dryland cropping and grazing, and the balance comprising timbered grazing and support land. 

•	Significant water entitlements include 4,610ML* of General Security, and 40ML* of Stock & Domestic.

•	The property has recently undergone extensive land forming works for high quality cotton production.

•	High quality operational infrastructure, structural improvements & productive soil types further enhance on-farm efficiencies. 

‘Warili’, Wilkins Lane, Warroo NSW 2871

•	Large-scale irrigated & dryland cropping property comprising 1,111* hectares.

•	First class irrigation development with 233Ha* of laser levelled flood irrigation, 58Ha* of flood irrigation, 633* of dryland cropping and grazing, 20Ha* planted to Jojoba and the balance comprising timbered grazing and support land. 

•	Significant water entitlements include 1,920ML* of General Security and 1,160ML * of Groundwater (Zone 5).

•	The properties have recently undergone extensive land forming works for high quality cotton production.

•	High quality operational infrastructure, structural improvements & productive soil types further enhance on-farm efficiencies. 

Bergen Park and Warili represent an unparalleled opportunity for a potential purchaser to acquire two large-scale, well designed and highly developed agricultural enterprises within 16* lineal kilometres of one another and close to nearby cotton gins at Trangie, Warren and Hillston.

Bergen Park and Warili are being offered in one line or as separate properties.

FOR SALE IN ONE LINE OR AS SEPARATE PROPERTIES BY EXPRESSION OF INTEREST CLOSING THURSDAY 23RD JULY 2020 AT 4.00PM (AEST)
